1
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:10,961
♪Love's little quiz
takes seven parts sweet♪

2
00:00:10,962 --> 00:00:13,559
♪And three parts bitter,
till you and I meet♪

3
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:17,159
♪I pretend I'm not there,
but secretly stay♪

4
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:26,399
♪Waiting for you♪

5
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:31,400
♪We've got so many
romantic dreams to unfold♪

6
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:36,224
♪Finally hearing
the I love you I long to hold♪

7
00:00:36,225 --> 00:00:39,839
♪Falling fast
into the swirl of your eyes♪

8
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:42,399
♪It's just too tempting, so tempting♪

9
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:45,499
♪Never could I have guessed♪

10
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:46,499
♪My heart's rhythm♪

11
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:49,632
♪How beautiful it is, meeting you♪

12
00:01:02,975 --> 00:01:05,961
=Late to Love=
(Adapted from "My Husband Is A Billionaire!")

13
00:01:05,962 --> 00:01:09,107
=Episode 20=

14
00:01:09,460 --> 00:01:11,060
As for Huo Group's transition,

15
00:01:11,219 --> 00:01:12,539
thank you for your concern.

16
00:01:12,540 --> 00:01:13,819
Let's wait and see.

17
00:01:13,900 --> 00:01:15,579
I hope everyone avoids speculation.

18
00:01:15,580 --> 00:01:16,939
If I see any false statements

19
00:01:16,940 --> 00:01:18,258
regarding our company,

20
00:01:18,259 --> 00:01:19,179
we reserve the right

21
00:01:19,180 --> 00:01:21,019
to pursue legal action.

22
00:01:23,219 --> 00:01:24,379
(Huo Beiyan,)

23
00:01:24,419 --> 00:01:26,939
(that's not what you told me at all.)

24
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:29,659
(You're carrying all this pressure.)

25
00:01:29,699 --> 00:01:31,739
(But every time you talk to me,)

26
00:01:31,779 --> 00:01:33,819
(you act like it's nothing.)

27
00:01:36,259 --> 00:01:38,299
(Are you overthinking again?)

28
00:01:38,660 --> 00:01:40,140
(Stop watching so much news.)

29
00:01:40,380 --> 00:01:42,060
(Focus on your research, Dr. Xu.)

30
00:01:42,419 --> 00:01:43,939
(Those old guys on the board)

31
00:01:43,940 --> 00:01:45,379
(are all bark and no bite.)

32
00:01:45,699 --> 00:01:47,700
(The media won't just make things up.)

33
00:01:47,940 --> 00:01:49,179
(The PR and legal teams)

34
00:01:49,180 --> 00:01:50,698
(Huo Group spends
millions on every year)

35
00:01:50,699 --> 00:01:52,140
(aren't there for decoration.)

36
00:01:52,219 --> 00:01:54,500
(You just focus on staying calm.)

37
00:01:55,940 --> 00:01:57,939
Hello, delivery.

38
00:01:58,339 --> 00:01:59,900
I didn't order anything.

39
00:02:01,180 --> 00:02:02,379
Your bubble tea.

40
00:02:03,619 --> 00:02:05,858
Half sugar, light ice, extra boba.

41
00:02:05,859 --> 00:02:06,980
Forgot already?

42
00:02:07,419 --> 00:02:08,738
You're such a dummy.

43
00:02:08,738 --> 00:02:10,599
Maybe we should come up
with a different code word.

44
00:02:10,599 --> 00:02:11,938
You look ridiculous doing this.

45
00:02:11,939 --> 00:02:14,459
No way. What if it's a bad guy?

46
00:02:14,460 --> 00:02:15,259
You...

47
00:02:15,619 --> 00:02:17,099
You don't even have a peephole.

48
00:02:17,619 --> 00:02:18,579
Fine.

49
00:02:18,580 --> 00:02:20,338
Now you have

50
00:02:20,339 --> 00:02:22,099
to play delivery guy.

51
00:02:22,700 --> 00:02:23,500
It's no trouble.

52
00:02:23,659 --> 00:02:24,460
Come here.

53
00:02:24,619 --> 00:02:25,620
Come here.

54
00:02:26,539 --> 00:02:27,659
Put that over there first.

55
00:02:29,099 --> 00:02:30,060
Wait a second.

56
00:02:46,099 --> 00:02:48,460
Don't judge it by how it looks.

57
00:02:48,499 --> 00:02:49,859
I wasn't slacking off today.

58
00:02:49,860 --> 00:02:51,658
While the equipment was running data,

59
00:02:51,659 --> 00:02:53,338
I looked up

60
00:02:53,339 --> 00:02:54,579
a recipe online.

61
00:02:54,580 --> 00:02:56,218
It seemed pretty easy.

62
00:02:56,219 --> 00:02:57,218
The only problem is...

63
00:02:57,219 --> 00:02:58,739
It's kind of ugly.

64
00:02:58,740 --> 00:02:59,880
But it actually tastes good.

65
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:01,220
I already sneaked a bite.

66
00:03:02,860 --> 00:03:04,538
You're not lactose intolerant, are you?

67
00:03:04,539 --> 00:03:06,620
I didn't think of that
until after I made it.

68
00:03:07,539 --> 00:03:08,620
Let me try.

69
00:03:21,219 --> 00:03:22,098
Wow. It's ugly,

70
00:03:22,099 --> 00:03:23,740
but it's really good.

71
00:03:25,339 --> 00:03:26,460
Good.

72
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:28,060
Have another bite.

73
00:03:35,619 --> 00:03:37,338
Now that you've eaten my food,

74
00:03:37,339 --> 00:03:39,218
you have to promise me

75
00:03:39,219 --> 00:03:40,659
something.

76
00:03:43,260 --> 00:03:44,139
From now on,

77
00:03:44,140 --> 00:03:46,058
whenever you're sure about something,

78
00:03:46,059 --> 00:03:47,859
whether it's through lawyers,

79
00:03:47,860 --> 00:03:49,338
onnections, or whatever,

80
00:03:49,339 --> 00:03:51,180
you have to tell me. Okay?

81
00:03:53,819 --> 00:03:54,658
I don't want

82
00:03:54,659 --> 00:03:55,739
to sit at home worrying

83
00:03:55,740 --> 00:03:56,658
by myself anymore.

84
00:03:56,659 --> 00:03:58,740
I'm really afraid
something might happen to you.

85
00:03:59,779 --> 00:04:00,460
I understand.

86
00:04:01,219 --> 00:04:03,419
First, I'll solve
the problem of you worrying.

87
00:04:03,420 --> 00:04:05,778
Then I'll solve the problem
of you being home alone.

88
00:04:05,779 --> 00:04:07,020
What's that supposed to mean?

89
00:04:08,300 --> 00:04:11,859
We could go on a real honeymoon.

90
00:04:17,380 --> 00:04:19,739
How's the mole investigation going?

91
00:04:21,940 --> 00:04:22,900
We've made progress.

92
00:04:23,179 --> 00:04:24,059
Don't worry.

93
00:04:24,339 --> 00:04:25,459
We'll have

94
00:04:25,460 --> 00:04:26,580
an answer

95
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:27,859
soon.

96
00:04:34,020 --> 00:04:35,059
Checkmate.

97
00:04:40,339 --> 00:04:42,338
I'm done. I haven't won a single game.

98
00:04:42,339 --> 00:04:43,900
Play with Beiyan.

99
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:50,499
Where are Beiyan and Nange anyway?
I haven't seen them in days.

100
00:04:52,299 --> 00:04:53,858
How would

101
00:04:53,859 --> 00:04:55,858
I know?

102
00:04:55,859 --> 00:04:57,619
Just asking.

103
00:04:57,979 --> 00:04:59,658
I haven't seen Beiyan in days.

104
00:04:59,659 --> 00:05:01,419
Feels weird.

105
00:05:02,339 --> 00:05:03,139
Stop

106
00:05:03,140 --> 00:05:05,059
worrying about them.

107
00:05:05,060 --> 00:05:06,218
When are you

108
00:05:06,219 --> 00:05:08,820
going to find someone yourself?

109
00:05:10,099 --> 00:05:11,700
You think I don't want to?

110
00:05:11,859 --> 00:05:13,739
I just haven't met the right person yet.

111
00:05:13,859 --> 00:05:14,899
Don't worry, Uncle Beixiang.

112
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:18,140
Once I start dating someone,
I'll bring her home for your to meet.

113
00:05:18,219 --> 00:05:19,220
Really?

114
00:05:20,299 --> 00:05:21,780
That's more like it.

115
00:05:22,460 --> 00:05:23,619
Come on. Set it up.

116
00:05:23,620 --> 00:05:24,900
Let's play another round.

117
00:05:25,179 --> 00:05:26,418
I'm out, Uncle Beixiang.

118
00:05:26,419 --> 00:05:28,419
You can figure it out yourself.

119
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:29,900
Look at you.

120
00:05:32,550 --> 00:05:38,657
(Huanfa Taste the World)

121
00:05:38,912 --> 00:05:40,307
(First Financial Weekly)

122
00:05:44,179 --> 00:05:45,379
As instructed,

123
00:05:45,380 --> 00:05:46,738
I tracked Mr. Zichen.

124
00:05:46,739 --> 00:05:48,819
I saw him and Miss Ye

125
00:05:48,820 --> 00:05:49,939
enter the same restaurant.

126
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:52,260
Got it. Gather all the evidence.

127
00:06:21,060 --> 00:06:21,859
Hello?

128
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:23,419
Hello.

129
00:06:24,419 --> 00:06:25,220
Nange,

130
00:06:26,020 --> 00:06:27,299
we've confirmed it.

131
00:06:27,419 --> 00:06:28,700
The mole really is him.

132
00:06:29,299 --> 00:06:30,939
Honestly, I had a feeling the day

133
00:06:30,940 --> 00:06:32,220
the lab was compromised.

134
00:06:33,060 --> 00:06:34,139
The system logs

135
00:06:34,140 --> 00:06:35,859
were wiped too cleanly.

136
00:06:36,099 --> 00:06:37,338
It was professional work.

137
00:06:37,339 --> 00:06:39,260
Not something
an ordinary person could've done.

138
00:06:40,020 --> 00:06:43,179
But I couldn't figure out the motive.

139
00:06:43,620 --> 00:06:45,220
Not until he brought over

140
00:06:45,940 --> 00:06:47,539
the flash drive.

141
00:06:48,299 --> 00:06:49,658
I never even mentioned that

142
00:06:49,659 --> 00:06:51,220
to my dad.

143
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:52,978
Turns out he was

144
00:06:52,979 --> 00:06:55,140
behind everything.

145
00:06:56,380 --> 00:06:57,299
Beiyan,

146
00:06:57,700 --> 00:06:59,619
are you upset?

147
00:07:01,940 --> 00:07:03,220
I'm okay.

148
00:07:04,859 --> 00:07:06,460
Honestly,

149
00:07:07,419 --> 00:07:09,220
I'm more scared than sad.

150
00:07:09,580 --> 00:07:12,418
Scared he'll hurt you to get

151
00:07:12,419 --> 00:07:13,900
what he wants.

152
00:07:15,060 --> 00:07:16,380
You know,

153
00:07:17,940 --> 00:07:20,218
Zichen has always been like the kid

154
00:07:20,219 --> 00:07:22,379
who works his heart out for a 99.

155
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:23,700
But everyone

156
00:07:23,859 --> 00:07:24,579
only notices

157
00:07:24,580 --> 00:07:26,059
the one who gets 100.

158
00:07:26,060 --> 00:07:27,499
I've always

159
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:29,780
been afraid of him getting hurt.

160
00:07:31,020 --> 00:07:32,659
This is just

161
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:35,460
another case

162
00:07:35,659 --> 00:07:37,299
of me winning.

163
00:07:38,179 --> 00:07:39,659
Once again,

164
00:07:40,419 --> 00:07:42,659
I've taken away what he values most.

165
00:07:42,820 --> 00:07:45,619
So he did all this

166
00:07:45,620 --> 00:07:48,419
just to prove he could beat you once?

167
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:50,820
I guess so.

168
00:07:51,179 --> 00:07:53,499
He's always lived in your shadow.

169
00:07:53,500 --> 00:07:54,298
But how could he

170
00:07:54,299 --> 00:07:55,658
gamble with the company your grandma

171
00:07:55,659 --> 00:07:56,819
built from scratch?

172
00:07:56,820 --> 00:07:57,659
Nange...

173
00:07:59,539 --> 00:08:01,419
I don't know how to explain it.

174
00:08:01,659 --> 00:08:02,499
But...

175
00:08:03,820 --> 00:08:04,978
I still want to give him

176
00:08:04,979 --> 00:08:06,380
one chance to make things right.

177
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:08,059
So what's your plan?

178
00:08:08,219 --> 00:08:09,859
I'm putting Dr. X

179
00:08:09,900 --> 00:08:11,539
in the spotlight.

180
00:08:14,580 --> 00:08:16,579
Beiyan hasn't noticed what I'm doing.

181
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:18,859
We've got enough time to bring him down.

182
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:20,939
I only have one question.

183
00:08:20,940 --> 00:08:22,700
Where's Xu Nange?

184
00:08:25,179 --> 00:08:26,379
If you'd told me from the start

185
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:27,738
that she was Dr. X,

186
00:08:27,739 --> 00:08:29,499
I wouldn't be in this position.

187
00:08:29,580 --> 00:08:31,059
You've got your own agenda.

188
00:08:31,060 --> 00:08:32,259
Don't think I don't know.

189
00:08:32,260 --> 00:08:34,259
You're afraid I'll push you out.

190
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:36,139
Huo Beiyan's been right

191
00:08:36,140 --> 00:08:37,458
under my nose the whole time.

192
00:08:37,459 --> 00:08:39,259
Even if I don't know
Xu Nange's progress,

193
00:08:39,260 --> 00:08:41,340
they still can't stop us.

194
00:08:42,179 --> 00:08:43,458
Right now, both we and Xu Nange

195
00:08:43,459 --> 00:08:44,619
are working in the shadows.

196
00:08:44,620 --> 00:08:47,139
Huo Beiyan's protecting her well.

197
00:08:47,140 --> 00:08:48,739
You need to move faster.

198
00:08:56,299 --> 00:08:57,499
He's making his move.

199
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:01,899
Today, Huo Group officially signed

200
00:09:01,900 --> 00:09:03,580
a strategic partnership agreement
with Dr. X.

201
00:09:03,980 --> 00:09:06,339
The two sides will work closely
in the field of neuroscience.

202
00:09:06,340 --> 00:09:07,600
Dr. X remains anonymous.

203
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,440
The public will see the results,
not the person.

204
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,219
Mr. Huo, how did you

205
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:12,259
establish contact with Dr. X?

206
00:09:13,579 --> 00:09:15,818
Dr. X is fully devoted

207
00:09:15,819 --> 00:09:17,019
to research.

208
00:09:17,059 --> 00:09:18,739
The decision to work with Huo Group came

209
00:09:18,740 --> 00:09:21,339
from trust in our ability to support
and develop those achievements.

210
00:09:21,340 --> 00:09:22,899
We'll do everything we can

211
00:09:22,900 --> 00:09:24,578
to help bring Dr. X's work

212
00:09:24,579 --> 00:09:25,979
to market.

213
00:09:28,740 --> 00:09:29,538
Mr. Huo.

214
00:09:29,539 --> 00:09:31,490
(The Irreplaceability of Dr. X)
That's all for today.

215
00:09:31,490 --> 00:09:33,058
Thank you all for coming.

216
00:09:33,059 --> 00:09:34,099
Huo Group will

217
00:09:34,100 --> 00:09:35,259
continue striving

218
00:09:35,260 --> 00:09:36,219
to deliver results

219
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:37,859
everyone can be proud of.

220
00:09:37,860 --> 00:09:38,739
Thank you.

221
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:43,339
What's your next move?

222
00:09:43,340 --> 00:09:44,818
I don't like being pressured!

223
00:09:44,819 --> 00:09:46,178
Pressure leads to mistakes!

224
00:09:46,179 --> 00:09:47,139
Relax.

225
00:09:47,140 --> 00:09:48,859
All the pieces are already in place.

226
00:09:48,900 --> 00:09:50,899
Mr. Wang and Mr. Li
have made their positions clear.

227
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:52,219
They'll challenge him at the next

228
00:09:52,220 --> 00:09:53,460
board meeting.

229
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:56,300
They're really willing
to take sides that quickly?

230
00:09:57,059 --> 00:09:59,619
Huo Beiyan has
deep roots in the company.

231
00:10:04,140 --> 00:10:05,660
When money's involved,

232
00:10:05,779 --> 00:10:07,379
there's no such thing
as absolute loyalty.

233
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:09,379
Suspending NIT-33 hit

234
00:10:09,380 --> 00:10:10,859
the biggest source

235
00:10:10,860 --> 00:10:12,259
of profit they had.

236
00:10:12,260 --> 00:10:13,418
Add in the shares I privately

237
00:10:13,419 --> 00:10:14,458
promised them,

238
00:10:14,459 --> 00:10:16,420
and it's enough
to make them take the risk.

239
00:10:18,620 --> 00:10:20,820
Huo Beiyan's persuasive.

240
00:10:21,059 --> 00:10:22,820
Don't let him talk them out of it.

241
00:10:25,699 --> 00:10:26,700
Don't worry.

242
00:10:31,020 --> 00:10:32,540
Huo Beiyan,

243
00:10:32,980 --> 00:10:35,019
I've prepared quite a surprise for you

244
00:10:35,539 --> 00:10:37,460
at the next board meeting.

245
00:10:49,860 --> 00:10:51,300
What's this?

246
00:10:51,740 --> 00:10:52,619
What's wrong?

247
00:10:53,059 --> 00:10:53,899
Mr. Huo,

248
00:10:55,319 --> 00:10:56,818
this is our team's resignation letter.

249
00:10:56,819 --> 00:10:57,739
Our vision no longer

250
00:10:57,740 --> 00:10:58,899
aligns with yours.

251
00:10:58,900 --> 00:11:01,460
We can't continue
with the upcoming R&D projects.

252
00:11:04,299 --> 00:11:05,298
Leave it there.

253
00:11:05,299 --> 00:11:06,420
Shen Yan will approve it.

254
00:11:07,299 --> 00:11:09,420
If there's nothing else,

255
00:11:09,539 --> 00:11:11,099
finish the handover and leave.

256
00:11:14,179 --> 00:11:15,099
Let's go.

257
00:11:15,620 --> 00:11:16,619
Let's go.

258
00:11:31,260 --> 00:11:32,180
Come on.

259
00:11:33,220 --> 00:11:34,420
Your turn.

260
00:11:34,900 --> 00:11:35,818
Look what you've done

261
00:11:35,819 --> 00:11:37,339
to Huo Pharma's stock price.

262
00:11:37,340 --> 00:11:39,420
Do you have any idea
how much it's dropped?

263
00:11:39,819 --> 00:11:41,658
Is this why we

264
00:11:41,659 --> 00:11:42,379
backed you?

265
00:11:42,380 --> 00:11:44,139
Why we invested in this company?

266
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:47,698
NIT is basically printing money.
And you're refusing to sell it?

267
00:11:47,699 --> 00:11:49,859
Do you think investors are idiots?

268
00:11:49,860 --> 00:11:50,578
Beiyan,

269
00:11:50,579 --> 00:11:51,778
you have a responsibility

270
00:11:51,779 --> 00:11:54,340
to this board and our employees!

271
00:11:54,860 --> 00:11:57,340
We followed your dad and watched

272
00:11:57,579 --> 00:12:00,060
this company grow step by step!

273
00:12:00,980 --> 00:12:02,219
At this rate,

274
00:12:02,220 --> 00:12:03,859
you're going to sink the whole ship!

275
00:12:03,860 --> 00:12:06,180
And I'm not going down with you!

276
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:09,418
Beiyan,

277
00:12:09,419 --> 00:12:10,499
if you keep this up,

278
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:12,420
the company's finished!

279
00:12:13,380 --> 00:12:15,619
Huo Beiyan, I'm not negotiating!

280
00:12:15,620 --> 00:12:17,499
This is an ultimatum!

281
00:12:18,860 --> 00:12:20,580
Let me tell you something, Huo Beiyan!

282
00:12:20,659 --> 00:12:22,538
You're destroying your dad's

283
